metadata.name: Collector's Jersey #1
metadata.description: Collector jerseys are airdropped to anyone who collects a 1/1 artwork from me off the primary market! The jersey number coincides with the chronological order of when the 1/1 was obtained. The jerseys are customized if the collector chooses so. There will only ever be 100 collector jerseys. The design of the jersey will change every 25 jerseys. If a jersey is purchased off the secondary market, please reach out to me as we can re-customize the jersey per your request and refresh the metadata. Jersey owners will be subject to benefits and perks I think you might like :). All the best -Tommy
